Code preview of the table CON_合同租金拆分模板

drop table "CON_RentTemplate" cascade constraints;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: "CON_RentTemplate" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "CON_RentTemplate"
(
"RentTemplateID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"TemplateCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"TemplateName" NVARCHAR2(50) not null,
"CreateDate" TIMESTAMP not null,
"Mode" INTEGER default 10 not null,
"Default" INTEGER default 0 not null,
"StartTime" TIMESTAMP not null,
"EndTime" TIMESTAMP not null,
"Enable" INTEGER default 1 not null,
"Remark" NVARCHAR2(200),
"CreateBy" NUMBER(32) not null,
"CreatetTime" TIMESTAMP default SYSDATE not null,
"ModifyBy" NUMBER(32),
"ModifyTime" TIMESTAMP,
"TemplateBoothType" INTEGER not null,
constraint PK_CON_RENTTEMPLATE primary key ("RentTemplateID")
);

comment on column "CON_RentTemplate"."Mode" is
'10 :编辑中
20 :创建完成）';

comment on column "CON_RentTemplate"."Default" is
'1:为默认
0:未默认
';

comment on column "CON_RentTemplate"."Enable" is
'1:有效 0：无效';

comment on column "CON_RentTemplate"."TemplateBoothType" is
'1:标准和非标展位合同模板 2:广告位协议模板 ';
